{"tid":1133532,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"爺孫戀玩完！何艷娟宣布離婚：我們決定分開","createTime":"2019-05-01T06:36:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-06T05:53:57.000Z","uid":62424,"like":51,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"0a11871dc5810152deab1780e9527d17974d2653","tid":1133532,"uid":62424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T06:36:21.000Z","msg":"前港姐季軍何艷娟去年7月爆出爺孫戀，當時26歲的她與66歲的澳博營運總裁吳志誠入紙結婚，二人年齡相差40年，之後何艷娟更晒出戴着巨型鑽戒，人生更來個大躍進，成功躋身名流。不過佢今日忽然於社交網上載文字圖片，並寫道「我們決定分開了」，雖然佢未有指明「我們」係何人，但不禁令人聯想她與吳志誠是否離婚：「在和平和友好的情況下，我們決定分開了。並說好了大家再見亦是好朋友，並且彼此多謝大家和互相祝福。」 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n痴線相差40歲 唔係為錢 唔通真愛咩。恨錢恨到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1892045d32eff5531fb9c609b1a16d9cbfdbdcd","tid":1133532,"uid":131522,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T06:36:35.000Z","msg":"愛心打破零回覆"},{"pid":"f047f9882b7d43e1021835e24646770849d9c5cb","tid":1133532,"uid":169468,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T06:37:14.000Z","msg":"分身家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a431640592e4c08e5005219968735a995548ccfa","tid":1133532,"uid":161153,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T06:38:12.000Z","msg":"唔知分到幾多身家"},{"pid":"2d3e78a3aea1ceab2f7b56d5a37176dfbb803629","tid":1133532,"uid":129,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T06:38:37.000Z","msg":"Who?"},{"pid":"2df292f4056555bc8b8c51dcfb2b45f42ea072d2","tid":1133532,"uid":29942,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T06:38:48.000Z","msg":"分幾多錢身家呢D先值得報"},{"pid":"5a4b9f78cb8c0d3ddb2de8fe0f0f1df4c3775135","tid":1133532,"uid":810,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T06:38:59.000Z","msg":"袋袋平安"},{"pid":"d429418e552c4b9acc016c186f512990fccec1aa","tid":1133532,"uid":182222,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-0